    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's totally spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without that dealership price tag, this is the one for you. It's been my pride and joy, but it's time for a new home. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
