    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality FD3S chassis featuring the pinnacle of rotary development: the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine. This specimen maintains exceptional compression across all rotor faces, paired with a precision 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is preserved with original Bilstein dampers and staggered forged BBS wheels, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are legendary for. This unit is free of vacuum line degradation or heat-cycling fatigue in the engine bay, presenting in concours-grade condition with flawless paint depth and a pristine interior. A definitive investment-grade example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
