    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a collector-grade example that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or door ding. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen a drop of rain. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and the original factory floor mats are spotless. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder containing every service record from day one, all performed by certified master technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is equally immaculate. For the discerning buyer seeking a truly 'mint' specimen with zero compromises, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
